OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1782224343
OL,3,CTeenager accused of murdering nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old girl gives evidence at his
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FA teenage boy accused of murdering a
OL,8,Fnine-year-old girl has told a court of
OL,9,Fthe moment she was fatally stabbed.
OL,11,FAria Thorpe died after sustaining a
OL,12,Fknife wound to her chest at her home
OL,13,Fin Weston-super-Mare, North Somerset,
OL,14,Fon 15 December last year.
OL,16,FThe 16-year-old boy, who cannot be
OL,17,Fidentified due to his age, denies
OL,18,Fcharges of murder and manslaughter in
OL,19,Frelation to Aria's death.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
