FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1782224343
OL,3,CTeenager accused of murdering nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old girl gives evidence at his
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FGiving evidence to Bristol Crown
OL,8,FCourt, the boy said he had picked up a
OL,9,Fknife from the kitchen of Aria's home
OL,10,Fand went into the lounge where she was
OL,11,Fsitting on the sofa.
OL,13,F"Aria stood up and I was waving around
OL,14,Fthe knife," he told the jury.
OL,16,F"Then at some point I decided that I
OL,17,Fwas going to try to make her flinch
OL,18,Fand scare her, to get a reaction.
OL,20,F"I leaned forward, acted like I was
OL,21,Ffencing."
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@KO]xD@AOU|D@AOU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1782224343
OL,3,CTeenager accused of murdering nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old girl gives evidence at his
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FThe defendant said Aria had been in
OL,8,Ffront of him at the time.
OL,10,F"She had almost taken a step forward
OL,11,Fbut without taking a step forward
OL,12,Fbecause before she could, it
OL,13,Fhappened," he said.
OL,15,F"I don't know what she was doing.
OL,17,F"The knife went into her. Then I
OL,18,Fpulled it out. I didn't know what to
OL,19,Fdo. She put her hand to her chest."
OL,26,@rD@AOUuD@JO]wD@AOUyD@AOU{D@cO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1782224343
OL,3,CTeenager accused of murdering nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old girl gives evidence at his
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FThe boy said Aria then fell to the
OL,8,Ffloor on her front.
OL,10,F"I thought she had died," he told the
OL,11,Fcourt.
OL,13,F"I got scared, I panicked. So I ran to
OL,14,Fthe kitchen with the knife and I put
OL,15,Fit back into the sink."
OL,17,FThe boy then walked to a nearby train
OL,18,Fstation, where he told a group of
OL,19,Fchildren he had killed Aria
OL,20,Faccidentally.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@YO]uD@AOUwD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1782224343
OL,3,CTeenager accused of murdering nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old girl gives evidence at his
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FHe borrowed one of the children's
OL,8,Fphones and searched for "what happens
OL,9,Fif you kill...?".
OL,11,FAnother child rang police on 999 and
OL,12,Fofficers attended the station `
OL,13,Farresting the boy shortly after he
OL,14,Fboarded a train.
OL,16,FThe boy confirmed he had not checked
OL,17,Fon Aria after she was injured, had not
OL,18,Frung for an ambulance or raised the
OL,19,Falarm.
OL,26,@pD@YOUqD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
