PN,40906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1782224343
OL,3,CTeenager accused of murdering nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old girl gives evidence at his
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FAndrew Langdon KC, representing the
OL,8,Fboy, asked how he was feeling about
OL,9,Fwhat had happened.
OL,11,F"I felt horrible," the boy replied.
OL,13,FThe following day, the boy gave a
OL,14,Fprepared statement to police officers
OL,15,Fduring an interview.
OL,17,FThis stated he had "stabbed her in the
OL,18,Fchest" and was not sure why.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@RO]yD@TOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1782224343
OL,3,CTeenager accused of murdering nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old girl gives evidence at his
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FMr Langdon asked why the statement did
OL,8,Fnot reference that it had been an
OL,9,Faccident.
OL,11,FThe boy said: "All I thought was I was
OL,12,Fthe one who murdered Aria and all I
OL,13,Fwanted to do was admit guilt to it.
OL,15,F"I just said that I stabbed her and
OL,16,Fthat was it. I just took the blame
OL,17,Fbecause it was my fault."
OL,26,@sD@OOUwD@AOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
