OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1782224343
OL,3,CTeenager accused of murdering nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old girl gives evidence at his
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FOn Thursday, Home Office pathologist
OL,8,FDr Amanda Jeffery told the court Aria
OL,9,Fdied as a result of a single stab
OL,10,Fwound to her chest, which went through
OL,11,Fher heart.
OL,13,FDr Jeffery added that Aria would have
OL,14,Fdied "very swiftly" from the injury.
OL,16,FAria attended school on the day of her
OL,17,Fdeath and was collected from an after-
OL,18,Fschool dance class by her mother, Tori
OL,19,FHull, at about 4.30pm.
OL,26,@vD@FOUvD@SO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1782224343
OL,3,CTeenager accused of murdering nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old girl gives evidence at his
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FThey went shopping for mini-pizzas and
OL,8,Ftoppings, which they made together. Ms
OL,9,FHull left for an evening work shift
OL,10,Fshortly after, with Aria watching
OL,11,FYouTube videos on the television.
OL,13,FFamily friend Ollie Sheppard, who was
OL,14,Fstaying temporarily at the house,
OL,15,Freturned there after work at about 6pm.
OL,17,FHe found Aria on the floor of the
OL,18,Fliving room and rang 999, with police
OL,19,Fand paramedics arriving a short time
OL,20,Flater.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
