OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1782224343
OL,3,CTeenager accused of murdering nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old girl gives evidence at his
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FTragically, Aria could not be saved
OL,8,Fand was pronounced dead at 6.58pm.
OL,10,FThe boy denies the charges of murder
OL,11,Fand manslaughter. The trial, before
OL,12,FMrs Justice O'Farrell, continues.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
